wdi-GC.REV.SOCL.CN.def: Social contributions include social security contributions by employees, employers, and self-employed individuals, and other contributions whose source cannot be determined. They also include actual or imputed contributions to social insurance schemes operated by governments.
wdi-GC.REV.SOCL.CN.name: Social contributions
wdi-GC.REV.SOCL.CN.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.
